text: "I Won't Hold You Back" is a 1983 song by American rock band Toto. It is from their fourth studio album Toto IV. It went to number 11 in Ireland, number 10 in the United States and number 17 in Canada. It was later sampled by Roger Sanchez for his song Another Chance. ==References== Category:1983 songs Category:1980s ballads Category:Rock ballads Category:Toto (band) songs
title: I Won't Hold You Back
